maintainers         artisancomputer.com:zdw
description         Utility library for gitignore style pattern matching of file paths.
long_description \
    pathspec is a utility library for pattern matching of file paths. So far this only includes Git’s wildmatch pattern matching which itself is derived from Rsync’s wildmatch.

